Give note, to Shaman leader (He is in &quot;Root of Innuruuk&quot;), wear all. Go to swamp. When entering swamp, take directly to the left, and pass the second basher, and stay there.<BR>
Thats a very good 'hunting-spot' to start at, kill some critters, you need like 2 yella shinies, then head back to leader, buy &quot;Burst Of Flame&quot; from leaders friend. Go back to 'hunting-spot'. Now you just pick monster-food with &quot;burst of flame&quot;, not so much runner anymore. Depending on how many Trolls there are in da area, you will hit LV 5, in no time, app 3 Hrs. And also use second Basher if in trouble, he kill critters for you..wich means that you have close to safe-spot also...and if you die, you will be respawned at safe-spot....get da idea of hunting-spot greatness?<BR>
